18
00:01:10,740 --> 00:01:12,980
=Episode 4=

19
00:01:22,150 --> 00:01:23,150
Is Princess Yingge here?

20
00:01:27,350 --> 00:01:28,190
Come in.

21
00:01:33,470 --> 00:01:34,760
What brings you here, Your Highness?

22
00:01:37,870 --> 00:01:39,590
I have some ointment from the palace.

23
00:01:39,790 --> 00:01:41,310
I thought it might be good for your injury.

24
00:01:41,920 --> 00:01:42,760
So I brought it to you.

25
00:01:45,510 --> 00:01:46,350
Thank you, Your Highness.

26
00:01:49,900 --> 00:01:51,420
(Prescription)

27
00:02:02,480 --> 00:02:04,790
It's Imperial Physician Gu's handwriting.

28
00:02:05,920 --> 00:02:06,950
Do you know him?

29
00:02:07,850 --> 00:02:08,990
How did you get this prescription?

30
00:02:09,400 --> 00:02:11,280
Years ago, Physician Gu traveled to Yueying

31
00:02:11,680 --> 00:02:12,750
and saved my life.

32
00:02:13,430 --> 00:02:15,910
I found this in the secret chamber

33
00:02:16,240 --> 00:02:17,590
of the Third Prince's residence.

34
00:02:17,910 --> 00:02:19,150
So, your visit to my brother's residence

35
00:02:20,630 --> 00:02:22,680
was to investigate the case of the Gu family?

36
00:02:26,150 --> 00:02:26,990
Precisely.

37
00:02:27,470 --> 00:02:30,120
The savior I mentioned was Physician Gu.

38
00:02:30,910 --> 00:02:31,800
I'll take the ointment.

39
00:02:32,120 --> 00:02:32,960
Thank you, Your Highness.

40
00:02:34,240 --> 00:02:35,080
Good day.

41
00:02:37,520 --> 00:02:38,360
Princess,

42
00:02:38,630 --> 00:02:40,360
do you see anything unusual
in the prescription?

43
00:02:41,120 --> 00:02:41,960
I do not.

44
00:02:42,030 --> 00:02:43,400
If the prescription reveals nothing,

45
00:02:44,030 --> 00:02:46,470
maybe you should check the records
of the medical staff on duty that day.

46
00:02:47,470 --> 00:02:48,310
Finding that person

47
00:02:48,590 --> 00:02:49,870
might yield some answers.

48
00:02:54,680 --> 00:02:55,520
I'll be back shortly.

49
00:02:55,840 --> 00:02:56,680
You are still recovering.

50
00:02:56,710 --> 00:02:57,550
It's fine.

51
00:03:40,470 --> 00:03:41,520
Are you Huang Lian?

52
00:03:41,800 --> 00:03:42,800
I am.

53
00:03:43,280 --> 00:03:44,310
Who are you?

54
00:03:44,960 --> 00:03:46,430
Did you decoct and deliver the medicine

55
00:03:46,590 --> 00:03:48,280
prescribed by Physician Gu?

56
00:03:48,680 --> 00:03:49,590
I did.

57
00:03:51,000 --> 00:03:52,630
(Prescription)
Is this the prescription back then?

58
00:03:53,280 --> 00:03:54,190
Well…

59
00:03:54,360 --> 00:03:55,630
It was so long ago.

60
00:03:55,870 --> 00:03:56,800
I don't recall.

61
00:03:57,240 --> 00:03:59,710
The Gu family's massacre
was widely known back then.

62
00:03:59,870 --> 00:04:00,870
If you were truly uninvolved,

63
00:04:01,190 --> 00:04:02,150
why did you hide?

64
00:04:03,080 --> 00:04:03,920
It's true

65
00:04:04,240 --> 00:04:05,190
that I decocted the medicine

66
00:04:05,400 --> 00:04:07,590
according to Physician Gu's prescription.

67
00:04:08,080 --> 00:04:09,520
But after it was prepared,

68
00:04:09,750 --> 00:04:11,150
someone else snatched it.

69
00:04:12,430 --> 00:04:13,270
Who did it?

70
00:04:13,590 --> 00:04:16,160
An ordinary palace guard at the time,

71
00:04:16,510 --> 00:04:18,000
who is now General Jiang He,

72
00:04:18,430 --> 00:04:21,430
promoted by the Chancellor.

73
00:04:23,240 --> 00:04:24,120
The Chancellor?

74
00:04:25,510 --> 00:04:26,680
Why didn't you say anything back then?

75
00:04:26,800 --> 00:04:28,600
I was just a decoctor.

76
00:04:28,800 --> 00:04:29,640
Besides...

77
00:04:29,680 --> 00:04:31,480
Besides, you took their bribe, didn't you?

78
00:04:31,680 --> 00:04:33,480
I had to take it or die.

79
00:04:33,750 --> 00:04:34,680
I had no idea

80
00:04:35,240 --> 00:04:37,390
that the Gu family would be wiped out
because of that.

81
00:04:38,040 --> 00:04:39,070
I beg for your mercy.

82
00:04:39,560 --> 00:04:40,800
I had no choice.

83
00:04:41,160 --> 00:04:42,390
If I hadn't complied,

84
00:04:42,630 --> 00:04:44,510
my family and I would have been killed.

85
00:04:47,800 --> 00:04:48,870
Keep this secret,

86
00:04:49,830 --> 00:04:50,670
and I won't kill you.

87
00:04:51,830 --> 00:04:52,720
I will.

88
00:05:17,720 --> 00:05:18,560
Hold on a moment, lady.

89
00:05:20,920 --> 00:05:22,040
There's a price

90
00:05:22,390 --> 00:05:23,630
on your head.

91
00:05:28,070 --> 00:05:30,190
See if you can take it.

92
00:05:48,920 --> 00:05:50,870
(I must not die here.)

