104
00:06:47,800 --> 00:06:51,920
♪Just a bit longer?♪

105
00:06:52,090 --> 00:06:56,570
♪Cast our dreams into the fire's embrace♪

106
00:06:56,570 --> 00:06:58,970
♪Let them end with a final grace♪

107
00:06:58,970 --> 00:07:03,370
♪Burn away my memories of snow♪

108
00:07:03,370 --> 00:07:05,890
♪And the deceit♪

109
00:07:05,890 --> 00:07:10,210
♪Let me cherish one last look♪

110
00:07:10,210 --> 00:07:12,560
♪In your gentle gaze♪

111
00:07:12,720 --> 00:07:15,930
♪Our last kiss is so tender♪

112
00:07:15,930 --> 00:07:19,520
