113
00:07:20,430 --> 00:07:21,630
Don't kill me.

114
00:07:25,360 --> 00:07:26,200
Help!

115
00:07:30,560 --> 00:07:31,400
Help!

116
00:07:39,830 --> 00:07:43,040
Run.

117
00:07:46,070 --> 00:07:46,950
