126
00:08:20,070 --> 00:08:21,680
Someone sent a letter to my palace,

127
00:08:22,720 --> 00:08:23,750
asking me to come here for you.

128
00:08:24,600 --> 00:08:25,680
(It must be Dieling.)

129
00:08:31,120 --> 00:08:32,120
The Lantern Festival?

130
00:08:32,710 --> 00:08:33,870
How long have I been unconscious?

131
00:08:35,750 --> 00:08:36,600
A day and a night.

132
00:08:47,200 --> 00:08:48,870
- Bravo!
- Great!

133
00:08:50,520 --> 00:08:51,360
Amazing.

134
00:08:52,440 --> 00:08:54,000
Are you all right?

135
00:08:55,150 --> 00:08:56,120
Thank you.

136
00:08:56,720 --> 00:08:57,560
Did you hurt yourself?

137
00:08:57,750 --> 00:08:58,630
Did the lantern break?

138
00:08:59,240 --> 00:09:00,080
It's fine.

139
00:09:00,200 --> 00:09:02,320
If it's broken, I will make you another one.

140
00:09:02,840 --> 00:09:03,680
- Thank you.
- Thank you, lady.

141
