185
00:11:19,960 --> 00:11:21,390
Now, I am certain

186
00:11:22,120 --> 00:11:23,510
that no one is more suitable

187
00:11:23,510 --> 00:11:25,320
to be my ally than you, Princess.

188
00:11:26,600 --> 00:11:27,790
May we both

189
00:11:28,480 --> 00:11:29,840
